OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1771952662
OL,3,CHow Ukrainian pilots and the RAF are
OL,4,Cteaching each other to defend Europe
OL,6,FIt has been four years since the start
OL,7,Fof Russia's full-scale invasion of
OL,8,FUkraine.
OL,10,FAt the start of the war, some of the
OL,11,Fearliest help to Ukraine came from
OL,12,FBritain, teaching its military
OL,13,Ffighting techniques on weapons systems.
OL,15,FFour years on, in an undisclosed
OL,16,Flocation in central England, we
OL,17,Fwatched as two of Ukraine's top
OL,18,Fhelicopter pilots received training
OL,19,Ffrom the RAF on how to train the next
OL,20,Fgeneration of pilots on the front line.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
