FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1771952662
OL,3,CHow Ukrainian pilots and the RAF are
OL,4,Cteaching each other to defend Europe
OL,6,FWe witnessed the teacher-pupil dynamic
OL,7,Fchange, though, as it came to light
OL,8,Fthat the RAF is learning just as much
OL,9,Ffrom the Ukrainian pilots as it is
OL,10,Fteaching them.
OL,12,FThe last time the RAF was involved in
OL,13,Ffront-line combat was in Afghanistan
OL,14,Fand Iraq, but the war in Ukraine is
OL,15,Fnoticeably different.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
