OL,3,CHow Ukrainian pilots and the RAF are
OL,4,Cteaching each other to defend Europe
OL,6,FDrone warfare has changed how wars are
OL,7,Ffought - and the two Ukrainian pilots
OL,8,Fwe were introduced to, "Victor" and
OL,9,F"Bravo", have been on the front line
OL,10,Fin that battle, piloting helicopters
OL,11,Fas they attempt to shoot down Russian
OL,12,FShahed drones.
OL,14,FThat is something which the RAF has
OL,15,Fnever done in active combat.
OL,17,F"I've shot down more than 100 drones",
OL,18,FVictor told ITV News.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1771952662
OL,3,CHow Ukrainian pilots and the RAF are
OL,4,Cteaching each other to defend Europe
OL,6,F"It's a good point of our presence
OL,7,Fhere because we can give our
OL,8,Fexperience to the RAF and to UK
OL,9,Fpilots. It's like an exchange of
OL,10,Fexperience."
OL,12,FSquadron Leader Tom Brown said:
OL,13,F"They're coming from frontline
OL,14,Foperations where the way of warfare
OL,15,Fhas completely changed.
OL,17,F"So while we can teach them, they
OL,18,Fbring a lot to the party as well, in
OL,19,Fthe fact that they can teach us their
OL,20,Ftactics or give us their experiences."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
