OL,3,CHow Ukrainian pilots and the RAF are
OL,4,Cteaching each other to defend Europe
OL,6,FIn the RAF's state-of-the-art
OL,7,Fhelicopter simulator, Victor describes
OL,8,Fflying helicopters on the front line
OL,9,Fin Ukraine.
OL,11,F"There are many threats, there's
OL,12,Ffighters with weapons waiting for
OL,13,Fhelicopters and they're hunting for
OL,14,Fus."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
