OL,3,CHow Ukrainian pilots and the RAF are
OL,4,Cteaching each other to defend Europe
OL,6,FThe initiative is the first time the
OL,7,FUK has offered helicopter instructor
OL,8,Ftraining to Ukraine, building on the
OL,9,Fsuccessful fixed-wing instructor
OL,10,Fprogramme delivered to Ukrainian
OL,11,Faircrew as part of Operation
OL,12,FInterstorm.
OL,14,FThe helicopter instructor course
OL,15,Fequips experienced Ukrainian pilots
OL,16,Fwith the skills to train the next
OL,17,Fgeneration of rotary-wing military
OL,18,Faviators, multiplying Ukraine's
OL,19,Fability to develop its flying training
OL,20,Fcapacity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
