OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1771952662
OL,3,CHow Ukrainian pilots and the RAF are
OL,4,Cteaching each other to defend Europe
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIt's hoped the RAF will receive more
OL,12,FUkrainian pilots in the future to
OL,13,Fcontinue its support to Ukraine.
OL,15,FThe Commandant, Group Captain Mike
OL,16,FBrown, sees the programme as mutually
OL,17,Fbeneficial: "The last time I deployed
OL,18,Fon operations, it was to Afghanistan
OL,19,For to Iraq, and that is a very
OL,20,Fdifferent scenario.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
