FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1771952662
OL,3,CHow Ukrainian pilots and the RAF are
OL,4,Cteaching each other to defend Europe
OL,6,F"Times have changed, the operation
OL,7,Fenvironment has changed, the world's
OL,8,Fchanged. They've lived operations in
OL,9,Fthe contemporary environment that most
OL,10,Fof us haven't."
OL,12,FWith each passing anniversary and each
OL,13,Fnew initiative like this one, NATO and
OL,14,FUkraine are building a partnership in
OL,15,Fwhich pilots like these defend Europe
OL,16,Fevery bit as much as we help defend
OL,17,FUkraine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
